  "description": "<p>‼️LONG TERM TECHNICIANS NEEDED ‼️</p><p></p><p>🚇 Location: Kallang</p><p>⏰ Working Hours: Mon - Fri, 830am-6pm</p><p>💰 Pay: $1,800 - $2,500/MONTH</p><p></p><p>✨Would be an advantage if have a Diploma or relevant experience or training✨</p><p></p><p>📝Job Scope:</p><p>🪛 Interpret and follow assembly instructions, schematic diagrams, and technical specifications</p><p>🪛 Use hand tools and equipment for assembly tasks</p><p>🪛 Collaborate with engineering teams to improve processes and implement changes</p><p>🪛 Perform system rack assembly and testing, including troubleshooting when required</p><p>🪛 Support 5S and workplace safety practices</p><p>🪛 Lead and guide operators to meet quality and productivity standards</p><p>🪛 Complete all required documentation and records for production</p><p>🪛 Assist in basic electronics assembly tasks<br /></p><p>Interested Applicants, pls call 6031 4933 or email recruit@onehirestaffing.com</p><p>1. Full Name</p><p>2. Residential Location</p><p>3. Start/End Date</p><p></p><p>R1104563 (Tan Si Ni Shirley Gwen)</p><p>EA License: 25C3058 (One Hire Staffing Pte Ltd)</p><p></p>",
